<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="16" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,151,464]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,404,428]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Remarks.</emphasis>
Judging from illustrations in 
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoux" box="[654,822,404,428]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refString="Ledoux, J. - C. (2004) Araignees de l'ile de La Reunion: I. Hahniidae, Ctenidae, Thomisidae et Clubionidae (Araneae). Revue Arachnologique, 14, 159 - 191." type="journal article" year="2004">
Ledoux (
<number box="[755,814,404,428]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="2004.0">2004</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
<taxonomicName authority="Simon, 1898" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1898" box="[830,1103,404,428]" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Prepotelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[830,950,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Prepotelus</emphasis>
Simon, 
<number box="[1047,1103,404,428]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1898.0">1898</number>
</taxonomicName>
might be a synonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Geraesta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Geraesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
